title: Sean Carlson from FYF Fest
itunes:title: Sean Carlson from FYF Fest
description:
I sat down with an old friend, Sean Carlson, who runs the very successful music festival called FYF here in downtown Los Angeles and spoke about inspiration, pulling pranks and criticism. We hung out with his dogs and incoming calls about booking shows so please pardon any interruptions you may hear.
